item.title: Google Summer of Code(GSOC) 2018
item.author: rishabh0402@gmail.com (Rishabh Chaudhary)
item.description: Google Summer of Code(GSOC) 2018 result was announced on April 23 at 09:30PM. I got selected for GSOC 2018 in organization The Libreswan Project. My project is Web based Certificate and Profile User Interface. I am really happy, It means a lot to me. Special thanks to Manoj Kumar (The motivator), Gurpreet singh and Lokesh sharma . These guys helped me a lot in making this possible and also my family and friends who always encouraged and helped me in my bad times.
